    <h2>2. What Additional Pages did you add?</h2>
        <li>
            <strong>Tea Quiz:</strong> 
            <p>Description: A quiz that provides customers with the perfect tea to match their preferences.</p>
            <p>Location: /store/quiz</p>
            <p>How to use: Answer the quiz questions, and press "Find My Tea" to recieve a tea recommendation.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Tea Blender:</strong> 
            <p>Description: Customers can create their own custom blends, by adding flavors so t\our store blends.</p>
            <p>Location: /store/tea-blender</p>
            <p>How to use: Choose a name for the bland, Select a base tea, add flavors, and click "Create Blend" to add the tea to your own custom blends.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Tea Map:</strong> 
            <p>Description:An interactive map showing the origins of our teas.</p>
            <p>Location: /store/map</p>
            <p>How to use: Click on markers to see a viriety of teas from different regions all over the world.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Reviews:</strong> 
            <p>Description:A page where customers can leave and view product reviews.</p>
            <p>Location: /store/reviews</p>
            <p>How to use: Read the existing reviews on the page. Click "Add a Review" to add a review</p>
        </li>

